structure.unit: A CABINET FOR HEALTH AND FAMILY SERVICES

law.text:
As used in this chapter, unless the context requires otherwise:
"Cabinet" means the Cabinet for Health and Family Services; and
"Secretary" means the secretary for health and family services.
law.history: Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 150, effective June 20, 2005. -- Created 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1998.
